HEADWORD: Footbreadth
<hw>Foot"breadth`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The breadth of a
foot; -- used as a measure.</def> <rj><au>Longfellow.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

